---
description: "UI + asset loading guardrails"
globs: ["**/UI/**", "**/*UI*.cs", "**/*Addressable*.cs", "Assets/Resources/**"]
---

# UI & Assets Standards

- UI framework: UI Toolkit by default.
- Prefer data binding for UI state synchronization whenever practical.
- UGUI/TextMeshPro is fallback-only for unsupported or legacy cases.
- Runtime loading: Addressables by default.
- `Resources.Load` allowed only for `Assets/Resources/Data/*`.
